          <hr>
          <p>
            Sleepy Ridge golf course will give you a unique golfing experience in the heart of Utah valley along the Eastern shores of Utah Lake. 
            We have something special at Sleepy Ridge Golf Course that recreates a long awaited trip to Scotland playing on a fabulous links style golf course. 
            Set the tone of the day by driving up to the beautiful three-story clubhouse that overlooks the links-stunning layout, with wetlands evident throughout the course. 
            The old country inspiration comes across in many ways during your 18 holes round of golf, with much of the course exhibiting reminders of Scottish links golf. 
            Before, during, or after your round grab a sandwich and beverage from State Street Grill and 
            relax with your friends in front of the two flat screen TV’s in the Heritage room or Pro Shop.
          </p>
