          <hr>
          <p>
            Crater Springs golf (formally Homestead) located only 20 minutes from Sundance, is a par 72 course measuring 7,017 yards 
            from the back tees and plays 5,091 yards from the forward tees. Course rating is 73.0 from the back tees and 68.2 from the forward.
          </p>
